{"tid":1389850,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［遍地開花］8月4日 台南文創園區 香港加油展覽","createTime":"2019-07-31T04:01:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T06:31:56.000Z","uid":134422,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"b24ba31fa5c078cb682c78cba932212c2862fa8d","tid":1389850,"uid":134422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T04:01:14.000Z","msg":"我畫咗幾幅有關反送中嘅畫，亦開咗個ig ac同連登post （如下）<br />\n<br />\nig: kel.illustration <br />\n<br />\n連登post ：<br />\n用畫筆記錄香港的事<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1363168\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1363168</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n啱啱收到一個在台港人嘅dm，佢將會喺8月4日（星期日）於藍晒圖文創園區聚珍台灣書店舉辦一個「香港加油」小型展覽，展示有關今次反送中嘅資訊同內容、亦會展覽有關反送中嘅畫作。<br />\n<br />\n收到的dm，如下: <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4LQCM5F.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4LQCM5F.png&h=b50af453&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果有身在台南 / 準備去台南嘅同路人，都可以去支持下。<br />\n遍地開花，香港加油！"},{"pid":"4073f998f093118d0e15c9ce1c8fd48554d63b4a","tid":1389850,"uid":134422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T04:03:46.000Z","msg":"香港加油"},{"pid":"13327e684210de82c44e62150d04850978e7f137","tid":1389850,"uid":134422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T04:04:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"335f46cd5943d1f4d84819b33610d25d55f4442e","tid":1389850,"uid":134422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T04:08:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6e18e5f2390f222d8849add07718553dc12ad9f7","tid":1389850,"uid":134422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T04:09:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a9ec455f3c98f082b2c69b0b47c7ae5b76db084c","tid":1389850,"uid":134422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T04:45:29.000Z","msg":"附上台南連儂牆照片<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YtwKspK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYtwKspK.png&h=e7a24b2c&s={SIZE}\" /><img s